{
  "chapter": 184,
  "chapter_summary": "项少龙与善柔追杀田单，田单自刎身亡，善柔姊妹大仇得报。众人乘船返回寿春，善柔答应随行回咸阳。项少龙应邀前往滇国，帮助庄夫人母子攻打叛军盘踞的高泽城。项少龙率精兵团从后山攀崖突袭，成功攻破城池，叛军首领之子李期宁死不降被射杀。收复高泽后，项少龙赶回咸阳，途中得知丞相徐先被吕不韦暗害致死。回到咸阳后，上将军鹿公因悲愤病危，临终紧握项少龙和小盘之手，托付二人保储君、杀奸贼为他和徐先报仇，随即撒手归天。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_dan",
      "speaker_name": "田单",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "好！你终于赶上我了！",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 184,
      "line_start": 32,
      "line_end": 32
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shan_rou",
      "speaker_name": "善柔",
      "listener": "char_tian_dan",
      "text": "田单！你知我是谁吗？",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 184,
      "line_start": 34,
      "line_end": 34
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "赵致",
      "listener": "char_tian_dan",
      "text": "当日你诛我三族之时，曾否想过有今天的一日？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 184,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 40
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shan_rou",
      "speaker_name": "善柔",
      "listener": "char_zhao_zhi",
      "text": "他是我的，我要亲手杀他！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 184,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhao_zhi",
      "text": "让你柔姊动手吧！",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 184,
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 44
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_dan",
      "speaker_name": "田单",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我田单生平杀人无数，哪记得曾杀过什么人？项少龙！算你本事，我田单服你了！",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 184,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 50
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_teng_yi",
      "speaker_name": "滕翼",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我们走！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 184,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 60
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "赵致",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "项郎！柔姊肯陪我们回咸阳哩！",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 184,
      "line_start": 74,
      "line_end": 74
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_shan_rou",
      "text": "那天你说的是骗我的了！",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 184,
      "line_start": 76,
      "line_end": 76
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shan_rou",
      "speaker_name": "善柔",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "早说过是骗你的，想来真气人！你竟一点都不着紧。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 184,
      "line_start": 78,
      "line_end": 80
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_yan_ran",
      "speaker_name": "纪嫣然",
      "listener": "char_shan_rou",
      "text": "柔姊莫要气恼，我们的夫君大人什么事都藏在心内，口硬心软，你切莫见怪啊！",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 184,
      "line_start": 82,
      "line_end": 84
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shan_rou",
      "speaker_name": "善柔",
      "listener": "char_ji_yan_ran",
      "text": "他是你们的夫君大人吧！与我善柔何干？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 184,
      "line_start": 86,
      "line_end": 88
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_lou_wu_xin",
      "text": "此城最厉害处是靠山之险，我们就由这处入手，保证三天后便可破城，因为世上没有一座山是爬不上去的。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 184,
      "line_start": 112,
      "line_end": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_yan_ran",
      "speaker_name": "纪嫣然",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "单看情况便知道它只是一个靠武力维持的政权，居民都是被鞭子强逼去做搬运的劳工。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 184,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 146
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shan_rou",
      "speaker_name": "善柔",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "算你这家伙有点办法！",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 184,
      "line_start": 162,
      "line_end": 162
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_teng_yi",
      "speaker_name": "滕翼",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "二哥手痒了，要先行一步。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 184,
      "line_start": 172,
      "line_end": 172
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_teng_yi",
      "text": "一起下去吧！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 184,
      "line_start": 174,
      "line_end": 174
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "乌家战士",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "城破了！城破了！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 184,
      "line_start": 186,
      "line_end": 186
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "乌家战士",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "弃械蹲地者不杀！弃械蹲地者不杀！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 184,
      "line_start": 210,
      "line_end": 212
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhuang_kong",
      "speaker_name": "庄孔",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "立即投降，否则杀无赦！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 184,
      "line_start": 244,
      "line_end": 244
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_qi",
      "speaker_name": "李期",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我乃李令之子李期，宁死不降！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 184,
      "line_start": 246,
      "line_end": 246
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lou_wu_xin",
      "speaker_name": "楼无心",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "此子作恶多端，曾奸淫妇女无数，死不足惜。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 184,
      "line_start": 248,
      "line_end": 250
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_lou_wu_xin",
      "text": "你倒知我心意，这处由你主持吧！",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 184,
      "line_start": 252,
      "line_end": 252
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_an_gu_xi",
      "speaker_name": "安谷傒",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "徐相遇袭重伤，死在返回咸阳的归途上。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 184,
      "line_start": 264,
      "line_end": 264
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_an_gu_xi",
      "speaker_name": "安谷傒",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "此事已证实是春申君所为，楚人虽把春申君首级送上，又允割让五郡以求和，但我们岂肯就此罢休？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 184,
      "line_start": 272,
      "line_end": 274
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_an_gu_xi",
      "text": "若是如此，就正中吕不韦的奸计。现在他是要利用国家危急的形势来扩大自己的权力。杀徐相的真凶是吕不韦，春申君只是被他扯线的傀儡罢了！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 184,
      "line_start": 276,
      "line_end": 280
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_an_gu_xi",
      "speaker_name": "安谷傒",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "什么？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 184,
      "line_start": 282,
      "line_end": 282
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_ling",
      "speaker_name": "王陵",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "快去见上将军最后一面！他一直牵念着你，不肯咽下最后一口气。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 184,
      "line_start": 300,
      "line_end": 302
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_bu_wei",
      "speaker_name": "吕不韦",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "少龙回来就好了，快进去见上将军最后一面。",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 184,
      "line_start": 316,
      "line_end": 318
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_pan",
      "speaker_name": "小盘",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "太傅快进来！",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 184,
      "line_start": 324,
      "line_end": 326
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_pan",
      "speaker_name": "小盘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "扶丹儿小姐出去吧。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 184,
      "line_start": 330,
      "line_end": 330
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_gong",
      "speaker_name": "鹿公",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "徐先是否被那奸贼害死的？",
      "tone": "颤声",
      "chapter": 184,
      "line_start": 344,
      "line_end": 344
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_gong",
      "speaker_name": "鹿公",
      "listener": "char_xiao_pan",
      "text": "保储君，杀奸贼，为我和徐先报仇，谨记！谨记！",
      "tone": "颤声",
      "chapter": 184,
      "line_start": 348,
      "line_end": 350
    }
  ],
